snippet.title: Vultures: Scavengers of Death - Official Demo Launch Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Check out the demo launch trailer for Vultures: Scavengers of Death, an adventure survival horror roguelike game developed by Team Vultures. Players will be recruited as operatives of the Vultures to scavenge the infested metropolis for materials and information that could cure the infection plaguing the world. Vultures: Scavengers of Death is coming soon to PC with a demo available now.
